If you dont have the file localy use this link under the head element
##<script type="text/javascript" src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.6.4.min.js"></script>

Add event (skickaBtn = button) (checkBeforeSending = method to launch) 
### $(skickaBtn).click(checkBeforeSending);    

Remove default Event (skickaBtn is the button of the type 'submit')
##### $(skickaBtn).click(function(event){    
        event.preventDefault();
        });

This is to prevent any jQuery code from running before the document 
is finished loading (is ready).
#####$(document).ready(function(){
   // jQuery functions go here...
});